<template>
<div class='min-h-screen bg-slate-50 text-slate-700 font-sans'><main class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 space-y-12'><section class='space-y-6'><div class='text-center space-y-3'><h1 class='text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 tracking-tight'>Girls code program Impact Report</h1><p class='text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-600'>From hesitant first steps to hands-on builders. Survey results show substantial gains in skills, confidence, and career momentum from Pre to Mid stage, with early post-program success stories emerging.</p></div><div class='grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6'><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 flex items-center gap-4'><div class='flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><rect x='4' y='10' width='3' height='8' rx='1'/><rect x='10.5' y='6' width='3' height='12' rx='1'/><rect x='17' y='12' width='3' height='6' rx='1'/></svg></div><div><div class='text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>67%</div><div class='text-sm text-slate-500'>Built a web app by Mid (4 of 6), up from 0% at Pre (0 of 6 answered)</div></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 flex items-center gap-4'><div class='flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M9 12l2 2 4-4'/><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='9' stroke-width='2' stroke='currentColor' fill='none'/></svg></div><div><div class='text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>83%</div><div class='text-sm text-slate-500'>At least somewhat confident by Mid (5 of 6) vs 0% at Pre (0 of 5 answered)</div></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 flex items-center gap-4'><div class='flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M5 8h14M5 12h14M5 16h10'/></svg></div><div><div class='text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>100%</div><div class='text-sm text-slate-500'>Mid participants attended Resume Workshop (6 of 6), reporting multiple interviews</div></div></div></div></section><section class='space-y-6'><h2 class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800'>Key Program Insights</h2><div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-5'><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-2'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h1a1 1 0 011 1v16H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zM9 9a1 1 0 011-1h1a1 1 0 011 1v11h-3V9zM15 5a1 1 0 011-1h1a1 1 0 011 1v15h-3V5z'/></svg></div><div class='space-y-1'><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Rapid Skills Growth</h3><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Average coding test rose from 56.7 (Pre, n=6) to 64.5 (Mid, n=6) — a +7.8 point gain.</p></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-2'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M4 7h16M8 11h12M12 15h8M16 19h4'/></svg></div><div class='space-y-1'><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>From Learners to Builders</h3><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>67% shipped a web application by Mid (4 of 6). At Pre, none had built one.</p></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-2'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M12 3v3m0 12v3m9-9h-3M6 12H3m12.364-6.364l-2.121 2.121M8.757 15.243l-2.121 2.121M15.243 15.243l2.121 2.121M8.757 8.757L6.636 6.636'/></svg></div><div class='space-y-1'><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Confidence Shift</h3><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Confidence jumped from 0% (Pre, 0 of 5) to 83% at least somewhat confident (Mid, 5 of 6).</p></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-2'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M3 6.75A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 4.5h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 6.75v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0118.75 19.5H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 17.25V6.75zM6 7.5h12v3H6v-3z'/></svg></div><div class='space-y-1'><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Resume Workshop → Interviews</h3><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>100% of Mid participants attended; multiple reported interview invites and traction.</p></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-2'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M17 20h5v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4h-3m-4 6H2v-2a4 4 0 014-4h3m0-4a4 4 0 118 0 4 4 0 01-8 0z'/></svg></div><div class='space-y-1'><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Community & Belonging</h3><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Participants highlighted motivation and friendships as key drivers of persistence.</p></div></div></div></section><section class='space-y-6'><h2 class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800'>Participant Experience</h2><div class='grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6'><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-4'><div class='flex items-center gap-2'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6 text-teal-600' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M9 12l2 2 4-4'/><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='9' stroke-width='2' stroke='currentColor' fill='none'/></svg><h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800'>Positive Experiences</h3></div><ul class='space-y-4'><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M9 12l2 2 4-4'/><path d='M12 22C6.477 22 2 17.523 2 12S6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10z' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'/></svg></span><div><div class='text-sm font-medium text-slate-800'>Career traction from resume support</div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>The workshop gave me a real edge. Landed several interviews because of my new resume. – Rosura (Mid)</div></div></li><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M9 12l2 2 4-4'/><path d='M12 22C6.477 22 2 17.523 2 12S6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10z' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'/></svg></span><div><div class='text-sm font-medium text-slate-800'>Confidence and empowerment</div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>The program changed everything for me. I've never been this confident in my knowledge and intelligence. – Rosura (Mid)</div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>The program made me feel empowered because I was able to tackle difficult challenges. – Enas (Mid)</div></div></li><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M9 12l2 2 4-4'/><path d='M12 22C6.477 22 2 17.523 2 12S6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10z' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'/></svg></span><div><div class='text-sm font-medium text-slate-800'>Belonging and motivation</div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>It's been a place where I feel motivated and confident in myself. I also have built friendships with girls that have the same interests as me. – Triana (Mid)</div></div></li><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M9 12l2 2 4-4'/><path d='M12 22C6.477 22 2 17.523 2 12S6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10z' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'/></svg></span><div><div class='text-sm font-medium text-slate-800'>Post-program momentum</div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>Thanks to it, I've not only landed my first tech job but have since received promotions. – Rosura (Post)</div></div></li></ul></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-4'><div class='flex items-center gap-2'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6 text-amber-600' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M12 9v2m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86l-7.4 12.84A1 1 0 003.7 18h16.6a1 1 0 00.86-1.5L13.7 3.86a1 1 0 00-1.72 0z'/></svg><h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800'>Challenges or Negative Feedback</h3></div><ul class='space-y-3'><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-amber-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 9v4h1v2h-2v-6h1z'/><path d='M12 2L2 22h20L12 2z'/></svg></span><div class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Early-stage anxiety: Pre participants described feeling nervous, confused, or not confident starting out.</div></li><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-amber-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 9v4h1v2h-2v-6h1z'/><path d='M12 2L2 22h20L12 2z'/></svg></span><div class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Debugging hurdles: One Mid participant reported low confidence due to frequent debugging help needed.</div></li><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-amber-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 9v4h1v2h-2v-6h1z'/><path d='M12 2L2 22h20L12 2z'/></svg></span><div class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Consistency gap: One participant noted missed sessions and feeling overwhelmed, impacting progress.</div></li><li class='flex items-start gap-3'><span class='mt-1 text-amber-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 9v4h1v2h-2v-6h1z'/><path d='M12 2L2 22h20L12 2z'/></svg></span><div class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Uneven project completion: By Mid, 2 of 6 had not yet built a web app; at Pre, none had.</div></li></ul></div></div></section><section class='space-y-6'><h2 class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800'>Improvements in Confidence & Skills</h2><div class='grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6'><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-3'><div class='flex items-center gap-3'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M4 4h16v2H4zM6 8h12v2H6zM8 12h8v2H8zM10 16h4v2h-4z'/></svg></div><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>From Idea to App</h3></div><div class='grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-center'><div><div class='text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>Pre</div><div class='text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>0%</div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>(0 of 6)</div></div><div><div class='text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>Mid</div><div class='text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>67%</div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>(4 of 6)</div></div><div><div class='text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>Post</div><div class='text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>100%</div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>(1 of 1)</div></div></div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>This program has been a turning point for me. – Ying (Mid)</div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-3'><div class='flex items-center gap-3'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M9 12l2 2 4-4'/><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='9' stroke-width='2' stroke='currentColor' fill='none'/></svg></div><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Confidence Trajectory</h3></div><div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-center'><div class='bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4'><div class='text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>Pre (responses)</div><div class='text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>0%</div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>Confident or somewhat (0 of 5)</div></div><div class='bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4'><div class='text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>Mid</div><div class='text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>83%</div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>At least somewhat (5 of 6)</div></div></div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>I've never been this confident in my knowledge and intelligence. – Rosura (Mid)</div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-3'><div class='flex items-center gap-3'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-6 h-6' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M11 4h2v16h-2z'/><path d='M4 11h16v2H4z'/></svg></div><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Test Score Lift</h3></div><div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-center'><div class='bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4'><div class='text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>Pre</div><div class='text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>56.7</div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>Avg (n=6)</div></div><div class='bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4'><div class='text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>Mid</div><div class='text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-600'>64.5</div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>Avg (n=6) | +7.8</div></div></div><div class='mt-2 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 italic text-sm text-slate-600'>Average Mid recommendation was 8.0/10 (n=6), reflecting solid satisfaction.</div></div></div><div class='text-xs text-slate-500'>Note: All percentages use the number of respondents who answered each item.</div></section><section class='space-y-6'><h2 class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800'>Opportunities to Improve</h2><div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-5'><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5 space-y-2'><div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M13 4l3 3-9 9H4v-3l9-9z'/></svg><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Boost Attendance & Continuity</h3></div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Add flexible scheduling, make-up labs, and short recap modules to reduce missed-session gaps.</p></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5 space-y-2'><div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 2l4 8H8l4-8zm0 20l-4-8h8l-4 8z'/></svg><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Dedicated Debugging Labs</h3></div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Offer weekly code clinics and peer-debugging squads to build autonomy and reduce confidence dips.</p></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5 space-y-2'><div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M4 6h16v2H4zM4 11h12v2H4zM4 16h8v2H4z'/></svg><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Beginner-to-Builder Scaffolds</h3></div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Provide stepwise project templates and checklists so more learners ship a web app earlier.</p></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5 space-y-2'><div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 4a8 8 0 018 8h-3l4 4 4-4h-3a10 10 0 10-10 10v-2A8 8 0 1112 4z'/></svg><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Confidence Micro-coaching</h3></div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Integrate short reflections, wins-of-the-week, and targeted feedback to normalize struggle.</p></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5 space-y-2'><div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 2a5 5 0 015 5v1h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1v1a5 5 0 11-10 0v-1H6a4 4 0 110-8h1V7a5 5 0 015-5z'/></svg><h3 class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Alumni Mentorship Loop</h3></div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600'>Leverage alumni like those reporting jobs/promotions to mentor current cohorts.</p></div></div></section><section class='space-y-6'><h2 class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800'>Need to Know</h2><div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5'><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5'><div class='flex items-start gap-3'><div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z'/></svg></div><div><div class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Who responded?</div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1'>Pre n=7, Mid n=6, Post n=1. Metrics use only stage-tagged responses for each item.</p></div></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5'><div class='flex items-start gap-3'><div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 2a10 10 0 100 20 10 10 0 000-20zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z'/></svg></div><div><div class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>How are confidence rates defined?</div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1'>Counted as Confident if participants reported confident or somewhat confident. Pre responses were predominantly not confident.</p></div></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5'><div class='flex items-start gap-3'><div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M4 6h16v12H4z'/><path d='M7 9h10v2H7zM7 13h6v2H7z' fill='white'/></svg></div><div><div class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Resume workshop participation</div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1'>Mid: 100% attended (6 of 6). Reported multiple interviews; Post respondent also attended.</p></div></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5'><div class='flex items-start gap-3'><div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z'/></svg></div><div><div class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Recommendation signal</div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1'>Mid average: 8.0/10 (n=6). Distribution included strong promoters and one detractor.</p></div></div></div><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5 md:col-span-2'><div class='flex items-start gap-3'><div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-5 h-5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='currentColor'><path d='M4 4h16v2H4zM4 8h10v2H4zM4 12h16v2H4zM4 16h10v2H4z'/></svg></div><div><div class='font-semibold text-slate-800'>Data caveats</div><p class='text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1'>Some items were unanswered at Pre/Post; insights reflect only the responses provided for each question.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class='space-y-4'><h2 class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800'>Overall Summary</h2><div class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-3'><p class='text-slate-700'>The Girls code program is translating curiosity into capability. Between Pre and Mid stages, learners moved from zero app builds to a 67% build rate, raised average test scores by 7.8 points, and shifted from universal uncertainty to 83% reporting at least some confidence. Resume support proved pivotal, catalyzing interviews at Mid and contributing to job attainment and promotions at Post for at least one participant.</p><p class='text-slate-700'>Challenges remain around early-stage anxiety, debugging autonomy, and attendance consistency. With targeted supports — debugging labs, scaffolded projects, and flexible catch-up — the program is well positioned to compound these gains and expand equitable pathways into tech.</p></div></section><footer class='py-8 text-center text-xs text-slate-500'>Powered by Sopact, Inc</footer></main></div>
